reviewText: Since this popped up while searching for a dress for my little girl, I'd like to take the opportunity to say, you're all losers and need a life! That's all.

Where to begin? Kristina is hot there is no questioning that but the way that she presents herself in the video makes her less sexy then she has the abilty to do so. The opening three videos are her running around. No dialog. This is diapointing, but her tight body makes it all the more watchable. Then the fourth video is sad for the most part. She looks tired and her eyes tell her tale. Her husband at this point was abusing her and it shows in those sad eyes. Her body is whorn in one year from the child she gave birth to and from the abuse at home. This is all set to some very sad piano music. The director was simple in his directon. For the most part he makes you feel nothing for her in his poor poor direction and poor choice in no dialog and music selection. I gave this a 5 simply for her strengh that is shown in the last video not for the "sexy modeling" in the first three. I would buy this again just to watch the last video.

True, there is little nudity in this video...but the playful, teasing aspect more than makes up for it! And Kristina is gorgeous and you DO get to see her fully nude, so this is well worth the time and money, in my opinion!
Very little nudity in this video. It did have some full nudity in two segments at the end of the video.
THE TITLE SAYS IT ALL. LOOKS LIKE SOMETHING I SHOT IN MY BACKYARD,DON'T WASTE YOU'RE TIME OR MONEY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
